LUM WAY et al. v. UNITED STATES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 6, 1903.) No. 123. In Error to the District Court of the United States for the Western District of New York. Royal R. Scott, for plaintiffs in error.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Judgments of District Court affirmed.
